[Student "S"]
{NORTH decides it is unlikely that SOUTH is Aceless, so all he wants to know is the number of Aces SOUTH does have. 
He invokes RKC Blackwood.

Since no trump suit has been agreed, SOUTH bids as if \Ds, the 
last-bid suit prior to 4NT is agreed. SOUTH has two Key-cards plus the trump Queen, so she bids 5\S.

NORTH bids 6\D. 
If SOUTH had just one Key-card, NORTH would bid 5\D over the 5\C reply.}

